OL,3,CPolice investigating 'suspicious' fire
OL,4,Cthat damaged three caravans
OL,6,FA fire that damaged three caravans and
OL,7,Fa nearby premises in Somerset is being
OL,8,Ftreated as "suspicious", police say.
OL,10,FThe blaze happened on Beckery New Road
OL,11,Fin Glastonbury on Saturday night, 13
OL,12,FJune. No one was injured.
OL,14,FAvon and Somerset Police were called
OL,15,Fjust before 8.15pm and they attended
OL,16,Falong with Devon and Somerset Fire and
OL,17,FRescue Service.
