OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1781619074
OL,3,CPolice investigating 'suspicious' fire
OL,4,Cthat damaged three caravans
OL,6,FA pair of caravans were severely
OL,7,Fdamaged and a third was also affected.
OL,8,FThe wall of a neighbouring business
OL,9,Fpremises also sustained heat damage,
OL,10,Fpolice said.
OL,12,FSergeant Simon Lancey, of the
OL,13,FGlastonbury neighbourhood policing
OL,14,Fteam, said: "We are treating the
OL,15,Fincident as suspicious at this time,
OL,16,Fpending the outcome of ongoing fire
OL,17,Finvestigation work.
OL,26,@vD@MOU
