OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1781619074
OL,3,CPolice investigating 'suspicious' fire
OL,4,Cthat damaged three caravans
OL,6,F"The fire caused a significant amount
OL,7,Fof damage but, fortunately, nobody was
OL,8,Finjured. If this fire was started
OL,9,Fdeliberately, then that was an
OL,10,Fincredibly dangerous act.
OL,12,F"Neighbourhood officers will be
OL,13,Fcarrying out patrols over the coming
OL,14,Fdays to help those people affected and
OL,15,Fconducting enquiries in the area to
OL,16,Fsupport the investigation.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
