OL,3,CPolice investigating 'suspicious' fire
OL,4,Cthat damaged three caravans
OL,6,F"We would please ask any witnesses, or
OL,7,Fpeople with CCTV, dashcam or other
OL,8,Ffootage, to come forward and contact
OL,9,Fus online on 101 quoting reference
OL,10,Fnumber 5226163150.
OL,12,F"Alternatively contact Crimestoppers
OL,13,Fanonymously via its website or on 0800
OL,14,F555111."
